🚀 📘 NOTES — DOCKER → GCP ARTIFACT REGISTRY (GAR)
🧠 1. WHY WE USE ARTIFACT REGISTRY?

👉 To store Docker images securely in GCP

🎤 Interview Answer

“Artifact Registry is used to store and manage container images securely, which are later used for deployments in Kubernetes.”

🧠 2. WHY SERVICE ACCOUNT?

👉 Automation identity for:

Jenkins
Terraform
Scripts
🎤 Answer

“We use service accounts instead of personal credentials for secure and automated access to GCP services.”

🔐 3. SERVICE ACCOUNT SETUP
🔹 Created:
jenkins-sa
🔹 Roles assigned:
Artifact Registry Writer ✅
Kubernetes Engine Developer ✅
Storage Admin ✅
Service Usage Viewer ✅ (you added — correct)
🧠 NOTE

👉 Follow:

Least privilege principle

📂 4. SERVICE ACCOUNT KEY

👉 Downloaded:

key.json
⚠️ SECURITY

❌ Never push to GitHub
✅ Store locally / Jenkins credentials

🔐 5. AUTHENTICATION (VERY IMPORTANT)
🔹 Command:
gcloud auth activate-service-account --key-file=key.json
🧠 What happens?
key.json → gcloud → authentication established
🎤 Answer

“We authenticate to GCP using service account keys via gcloud CLI.”

🐳 6. DOCKER AUTH CONFIGURATION
gcloud auth configure-docker
🧠 Purpose

👉 Allows Docker to push images to GAR

📦 7. CREATE ARTIFACT REGISTRY
gcloud artifacts repositories create my-repo \
  --repository-format=docker \
  --location=us-central1
🧠 Important

👉 Must create manually (unlike DockerHub)

🏷️ 8. IMAGE TAGGING (CRITICAL)
🔹 Format:
LOCATION-docker.pkg.dev/PROJECT-ID/REPO/IMAGE:TAG
🔹 Example:
docker tag fresh-milk-app:v1 \
us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/<project-id>/my-repo/fresh-milk-app:v1
🎤 Answer

“We tag Docker images with region-specific Artifact Registry paths for proper storage and versioning.”

🚀 9. PUSH IMAGE TO GAR
docker push us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/<project-id>/my-repo/fresh-milk-app:v1
🧠 Flow
Docker → Auth → GAR → Image stored
🎤 Answer

“After tagging the image, we push it to Artifact Registry where it is stored and later used for deployments.”

🔍 10. VERIFY IMAGE
gcloud artifacts docker images list \
us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/<project-id>/my-repo
🧠 11. COMMON ERRORS (YOU FACED ONE)
